City of Mbombela Local Municipality spokesman, Joseph Ngala, said a notice has been issued to City of Mbombela residents that the Central Region Civic Centre and Hendrik Potgieter offices will be inaccessible to the public as there will be fumigation taking place. Customers can continue to utilise the other service centres like The Grove, Plaza and all the regional services. Customers are further encouraged to use available online platforms to access services during this time. ALSO READ: Head-on collision on R40 claims eight lives The Central Call Centre will also be inaccessible during this time so customers should use the emergency number: 0137533331. Services will be back to normal on Tuesday 7 July.